object.customQuery:
SELECT 
  batch.batch_id,
  src.* 
FROM (
  SELECT DISTINCT source_name, load_type, agency_nup, contact_email, contact_firstname, contact_lastname, contact_title, created, id, modified FROM "$$metal_schema".adm_contact_guidewire ) src
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id, 
        bls.target_table_name,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM "$$metal_schema".batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'Guidewire'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM "$$metal_schema".batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'Guidewire'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
) batch
  ON batch.target_table_name = 'adm_contactguidewire'

to_char(o_agency_contact_guidewire_id))
